performers.description: Super Tonic is a San Diego based anime and video game cover band formed in 2019 from UCSD Alumni. They love anime, video games, and music so they joined together to creatively combine their passions and share it with the world.

The Intermission Orchestra at UC San Diego is a student-run orchestra dedicated to bringing the music from video games, anime, and films to life!  In preparation to the much-anticipated AnimeFest 2025, we've prepared an array of selections for your favorite animes, and we're beyond excited to perform for everyone!
